UID:bat-202605091330-motionarts-gala-2026@bloomingtonarts.today
DESCRIPTION:$. Celebrate the completion of a wonderful semester of dance w
 ith performances by both our academy students and company dancers.\n\n2:00
 pm: Ballet students perform Symphonic Dances plus Contemporary\, Jazz & Ch
 oreography classes\, and Company Repertoire.\n\n7:00pm: MAD Co. & mini MAD
  present repertoire\, ballet variations\, and YAGP solos\, duets & group p
 ieces.
