BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Mamma Mia (2008)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260515T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260515T210000
UID:bat-202605151900-mamma-mia-2008-@bloomingtonarts.today
DESCRIPTION:$. Constellation Stage and Screen & BCT Present:\n\nCalling al
 l dancing queens and super troupers! Experience the magic of ABBA’s grea
 test hits on the big screen in this feel-good movie musical about a bride-
 to-be searching for her real father.  Based on the Broadway musical of the
  same name\, Mamma Mia! is a high-energy celebration of love\, friendship\
 , and timeless pop classics..
LOCATION:Buskirk-Chumley Theater
URL:https://buskirkchumley.org/events/mamma-mia-2008-may-15-2026
X-SOURCE:BloomingtonArts.Today
END:VEVENT
