BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Another Revolution
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260604T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260604T213000
UID:bat-202606041930-another-revolution@bloomingtonarts.today
DESCRIPTION:$. Kat and Henry\, two graduate students from opposing scienti
 fic disciplines\, are forced to share a lab at Columbia University in 1968
 . Amidst interpersonal differences\, a campus devolving into political cha
 os\, and the uncertainty and turmoil of the outside world\, they each disc
 over what it’s like to be thrown into someone else’s orbit.
LOCATION:Constellation Playhouse
URL:https://seeconstellation.org/mainstage/another-revolution/
X-SOURCE:BloomingtonArts.Today
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Linda Perry - Let It Die Here (2026)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260605T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260605T210000
UID:bat-202606051900-linda-perry-let-it-die-here-2026-@bloomingtonarts.tod
 ay
DESCRIPTION:$. Linda Perry is one of the most outspoken and recognizable a
 rtists of the past 30 years. Her massive hit single “What’s Up” with
  her band 4 Non-Blondes made her an icon. Let It Die Here is a look at a c
 ourageous woman as she navigates life-altering circumstances amidst gnawin
 g career decisions.
LOCATION:Buskirk-Chumley Theater
URL:https://buskirkchumley.org/events/linda-perry-let-it-die-here-2026-jun
 e-5-2026/
X-SOURCE:BloomingtonArts.Today
END:VEVENT
