BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:An Evening with Gianmarco Soresi!
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260618T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260618T210000
UID:bat-202606181900-an-evening-with-gianmarco-soresi-@bloomingtonarts.tod
 ay
DESCRIPTION:$. Gianmarco Soresi is a New York‑based stand‑up comedian\
 , actor\, and creator known for his sharp societal observations and spry\,
  energetic stage presence. He blends upbeat candor with darker comedic bea
 ts\, earning critical acclaim from NPR\, Esquire\, The Atlantic\, Buzzfeed
 \, ABC News\, among others\, and has performed on The Tonight Show Starrin
 g Jimmy Fallon\, The Late Late Show with James Corden\, Comedy Central\, a
 nd more.
LOCATION:The Comedy Attic
URL:https://www.comedyattic.com/events/129480
X-SOURCE:BloomingtonArts.Today
END:VEVENT
